These are Puzzles for 3x6 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: tea, 7up, iced-tea, sprite, juice, milk
House: craftsman, colonial, tower, gothic-revival, victorian, farmhouse
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, pall-mall, bongani, ritmeester, baccarat, fonseca
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is the tower house##1
 2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1
 3. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1
 4. the fonseca-smoker is the farmhouse house##1
 5. the colonial house is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 6. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
 7. the farmhouse house is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
10. the person drinking juice is the colonial house##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the colonial house##1
12. the person drinking milk is between the baccarat-smoker and the colonial house##2
13. the tiparillo-smoker is between the person drinking iced-tea and the victorian house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3   |     4      |    5     |     6      |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice  | milk  | tea | 7up  | iced-tea   |
| House           | gothic-revival | colonial | farmhouse | victorian        | tower    | craftsman |
| Cigar     | bongani    | ritmeester     | fonseca   | baccarat       | tiparillo | pall-mall       |

