.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-2::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: taxi, car, jet-ski, roller, scooter, boat
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, davidoff, aristoff, blend, chaman, oliveros
There are 6 different nationalities: american, egyptian, canadian, russian, argentine, polish
 1. the dunhill-smoker is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the person driving the boat is the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the roller is the polish##1
 4. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 5. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far left##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is between the dunhill-smoker and the argentine##2
 8. the blend-smoker is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the russian##1
10. the egyptian is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
11. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is the egyptian##1
13. the american is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3      |    4    |    5     |     6      |
| Transport      | jet-ski     | taxi | car     | roller    | scooter | boat     |
| Cigar   | dunhill | davidoff | blend | oliveros | aristoff  | chaman  |
| Nationality           | egyptian    | canadian    | argentine     | polish  | russian    | american |

