.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: thai, nigerian, polish, spanish, french, italian
There 6 different types of food: banana, blueberry, apricot, cranberry, watermelon, avocado
There are 6 different favourite colors: chestnut, pink, yellow, ivory, aquamarine, purple
 1. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the thai##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is the person eating avocado##1
 3. the italian is on the far left##1
 4. the italian is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 5. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the thai##1
 6. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
 7. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 9. the italian is the italian##1
10. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
11. the french is between the person eating cranberry and the person who likes aquamarine##2
12. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
13. the spanish is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
14. the spanish is on the right of the polish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |   6   |
| Nationality           | italian  | thai | french     | polish | spanish | nigerian |
| Food   | watermelon     | avocado      | blueberry | cranberry        | apricot     | banana |
| Color     | pink | aquamarine     | yellow   | chestnut          | ivory      | purple |

