.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: action, superhero, family, musical, time-travel, scientific
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: techno, soul, disco, country, indie, classical
The people have 6 different jobs:  coach, accountant, chef, mechanic, videographer, writer
 1. the fan indie is on the right of the writer##1
 2. the fan techno is on the left of the mechanic##1
 3. the accountant is on the right of the fan disco##1
 4. the fan indie is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan disco##1
 6. the fan disco is the coach##1
 7. the fan country is on the far left##1
 8. the person watching scientific movies is the fan country##1
 9. the fan classical is on the right of the mechanic##1
10. the person watching family movies is the videographer##1
11. the person watching action movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching family movies##2
12. the fan techno is on the right of the coach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |    4     |     5      |    6    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific       | musical   | time-travel   | superhero  | action | family   |
| Music-Genre           | country    | indie    | disco | techno      | soul       | classical  |
| Job         | writer | chef | coach   | accountant | mechanic       | videographer |

