 9. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
11. the person who likes pink is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
13. the person who likes yellow is between the person who likes ivory and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2

.:: Answer ::.
