.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-18::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: lily, balloon-flower, daisy, iris, rose, sunflower
City: hamburg, marseilles, hannover, new-york, liverpool, rome
There are 6 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, iced-tea, sprite, water, lemonade
 1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 3. the person drinking 7up is the person who growssunflower##1
 4. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person who growsrose is the person drinking lemonade##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is between the person who growsiris and the person traveling to marseilles##2
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
10. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
11. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
12. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
13. the person who growsrose is the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |
| Flower         | iris | sunflower | daisy   | balloon-flower    | rose | lily |
| City   | liverpool       | rome   | marseilles     | hannover | new-york   | hamburg      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea   | 7up | sprite | almond-milk  | lemonade | water    |

