.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-19::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: zinnia, lily, aconite, rose, poppy, bellflower
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: sports, romance, drama, western, superhero, animation
House: modern, wooden, futuristic, victorian, cape-cod, gothic-revival
 1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 7. the wooden house is between the futuristic house and the modern house##2
 8. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
 9. the person who growslily is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the far right##1
11. the person who growszinnia is the victorian house##1
12. the modern house is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
13. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |      4      |     5      |   6    |
| Flower          | zinnia | rose      | poppy | aconite       | lily | bellflower   |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero | animation | drama   | sports | western    | romance  |
| House   | victorian    | modern     | wooden      | futuristic       | cape-cod       | gothic-revival |

