.:: Puzzle 3x6-Level-2-20::.
6 different games are played: whist, monopoly, scrabble, chess, backgammon, domino
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, sports, drama, romance, action, martial-arts
The people have 6 different hobbies: drawing, woodworking, singing, cooking, board-games, collecting
 1. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 3. the person watching romance movies is between the person playing domino and the person playing whist##2
 4. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching family movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person playing chess##2
 7. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person playing domino##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is the person playing whist##1
 9. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
10. the person playing monopoly is on the far right##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person playing monopoly##1
13. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |    5     |    6     |
| Game      | chess   | scrabble | whist     | backgammon     | domino    | monopoly    |
| Movie-Genre          | action   | family         | sports  | romance   | drama     | martial-arts   |
| Hobby   | board-games | cooking        | drawing | collecting | singing | woodworking |

 